Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢飛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢面具 參上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.03,0:00:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 蚱蜢面具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 衝啊 蚱蜢面具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰這傢伙太投入了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 蚱蜢面具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣幹掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢鐵拳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛腿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧 別過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢必殺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰這傢伙 劇本裡根本沒這段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家的支持下 蚱蜢面具大獲全勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}後面 後面…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級變身 海參怪男
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特級變身 鯨魚怪男
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯨魚水炮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏賊 咔咔…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪華變身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.48,0:01:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新烏賊男 參上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.41,0:01:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們在做這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在將要放暑假時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和純一制定了某個計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:53.11,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}邂逅的一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:59.46,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如命中相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:07.28,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想要確定這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:11.97,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今天依舊陪君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.58,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}愛上你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.66,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.80,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心湖泛起陣陣漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:26.12,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻與你一同邁步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:29.16,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:33.12,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.81,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.72,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:43.96,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}宛如夢幻的時間流淌著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:51.91,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}渴望凝望你雙眸中的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.83,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:59.92,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:01.25,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:07.94,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的就把我叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要商量什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美術的作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼也畫不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再畫不出來的話就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:41.56,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(320,260)\t(0,800,\fs14)}棚町 薰篇\N\N前篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:41.56,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(319,295)\fs17\t(0,800,\fs16)}素 描
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:41.56,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(319,295)\fs17\t(0,800,\fs16)}素 描
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:41.56,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,650)\pos(320,260)\t(0,800,\fs14)}棚町 薰篇\N\N前篇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你擅長畫畫真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫抽象畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還挺有難度的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是從這裡望出去的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風景畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你畫畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你為什麼要坐這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是不用在意 可我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能畫好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼畫好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田 田中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這對笨蛋情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在說你和橘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校都這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在看不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了 早上的事不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很像笨蛋情侶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我明白已經交往了半年多的你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係還是和以前一樣好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但明白歸明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是覺得和平時沒兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事要等兩人世界時才能做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 我和純一獨處時…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做了些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 和交往前沒兩樣的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假也快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和橘去旅行怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再怎麼說這也是高中最後的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的暑假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經是高中最後的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想把回憶寫進青春的一頁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一想去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是泳裝還是浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至裸體都一樣喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的錢包可沒豐滿到可以去旅遊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說要去打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了賺取旅遊資金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要努力打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個 看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs16\1c&H9a6351&\bord1\3c&ffffff&}蚱蜢面具\N 英雄舞台秀\N 急招臨時工作人員！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台秀的工作人員…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒打過工 沒什麼自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢面具陷入難關時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫到他的就是大家的加油聲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聽好了 大聲地替蚱蜢面具加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們先來練習一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對 就是這氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就看大家囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 表演即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要好好看到最後哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏賊 咔咔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小看我新烏賊男大人的實力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇本裡哪有這樣的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒的觸手炮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新烏賊男 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 新烏賊男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 薰你認輸沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是新烏賊男大人的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 反派和司儀怎麼比蚱蜢面具還顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 看你們把表演搞成什麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣一半工資
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那麼拼命了 才只有這麼丁點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我們把工作人員給惹怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來這是一份工資優厚的好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被人家說以後別再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都怪純一做了劇本裡沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰不也做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是幫著蚱蜢面具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越想越不甘心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只能這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清幽的山莊 海邊的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都和夢一起消散了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去找另一份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用盡一切手段都要在暑假時去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買到夏季才有的特別口味了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客氣什麼 我推薦的絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下 留點給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你要喝到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 全喝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是最後一罐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(345,190)\fs18\fad(50,0)\bord0\1c&H8583ec&}售罄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,100)\fs16}暑期特別計劃 超便宜 巴士旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個價位 明天也能馬上出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羨煞旁人啊 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的暑假就只有壽司修行一個選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是深夜巴士的廉價旅行罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有愛的話 價錢就別太介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 哥們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了今年暑假也要獨守河邊看煙火的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你帶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這寶貝簡直是我的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暑假 我有我的壽司修行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥們也有自己的男人修行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 巴士旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.61,0:12:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天兩夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要過夜的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是我讓你去旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是指一日遊那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的兩夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是在車上睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好嚇一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶禮物給惠子你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於等到明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和純一的二人世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 我都在想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 我和純一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算實現了去旅行這個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 有什麼奇怪的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哦 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽誰先到巴士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 跑錯方向了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真壞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽就是比賽 懲罰遊戲選什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在發車了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著全買了限定版口味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 純一…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一有一定想要去的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得出來旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能去到薰想去的地方就已經很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 我們來玩剛剛的懲罰遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只可以吃巧克力的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不可以碰到我的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真是無聊的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然能 我做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在此休息20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs16}坐得腰都疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能休息了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直坐著果然很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是價格超低的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不含抱怨及奢侈浪費哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 對於我來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和薰一起出來旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會說一些討人喜歡的話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你還要買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還剩很多零食嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是限定口味的零食寶庫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好品嚐這些從來沒吃過的口味怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說不能奢侈浪費嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是另外一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是這裡特有的限定商品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了這個村就沒有這個店了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是奢侈浪費呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這裡是限定品的寶庫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西也得有個度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦 買那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些是給大家的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一些是給自己吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先把它們放到巴士上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身輕便了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要再買了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 把那麼多的零食帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被巴士的乘客們笑話的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 我做了完美的偽裝工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽裝工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個了 我們快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是這裡特有的名菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能不好好品嚐一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這個理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說休息到20分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 時間還很充裕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 再拖拖拉拉地就沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 乘客們都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們準備發車了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 來這裡吃是來對了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴士是停在這裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這輛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這輛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花紋不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是這輛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形狀不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被丟下了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 旅行玩得開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在到哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李還放在車上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先和旅行社聯繫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是輝日東旅行社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於現在不是正常的營業時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰沙 再也吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…薰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們 現在是在兩人世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 正如純一說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的我們 的確過上了兩人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:34.53,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}清晨傳來腳踏車的清脆鈴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:40.18,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}彷彿告訴著我時間逐漸流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:46.07,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這份無法消散的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:51.38,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}下定決心把它交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.57,0:23:03.39,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}點綴未來的預想於我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:09.46,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}暗自祈禱當中有你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:14.42,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}於深秋落葉時深呼吸一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:21.97,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}嘴裡吐出的卻是絲絲的嘆息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:29.48,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}現在只希望你能聽我說一句
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:32.50,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:36.50,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這便是我的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是惠子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 旅行玩得開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有發生什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.64,0:23:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好奇 很好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 不要再刺激她好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個了 相信你已經買好禮物給我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你忘記了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:23:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 發生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:23:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想聽聽你們旅途的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事可填不飽肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只知道吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 旅伴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.20,0:24:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊
